      "comment": "IDEAL BEACH (7) was very brave in the APG 3CG Sales Classic at this circuit and distance last time, racing three wide without cover from a back row draw but boxing on for a 3.8m second. Draws wide but won his only third up attempt so should be at his peak. IM CATEGORY FIVE (3) is in good form and has the hoof on the till after coming from this barrier to place at her last two appearances at this circuit and distance. Consistent filly who is race fit now and could break through. IN RARE AIR NZ (6) draws wider but boxed on for third in a Group Three here last week. AMERICAN MACHINE (5) is first up since scoring at Pinjarra seven months ago. Worth keeping safe.",
